				<div id="post-8089" class="post-8089 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-alternative-energy tag-battery-back-up tag-emergency-power tag-steven-harris">
					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-1039- Steven Harris on Battery Back Up Systems Part 1 of 2</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-1038-steven-harris-on-battery-back-up-systems-part-1-of-2" title="12:32 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">December 12, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-1038-steven-harris-on-battery-back-up-systems-part-1-of-2#comments" title="Comment on Episode-1039- Steven Harris on Battery Back Up Systems Part 1 of 2">35 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<div id="tweetbutton8089" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fepisode-1038-steven-harris-on-battery-back-up-systems-part-1-of-2&amp;text=Episode-1039-%20Steven%20Harris%20on%20Battery%20Back%20Up%20Systems%20Part%201%20of%202&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fepisode-1038-steven-harris-on-battery-back-up-systems-part-1-of-2" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
