		<div class="comment-body"><p>Exactly it is far more a function of the charger then the generator.  A 2000 or 3000 watt honda both have way more horsepower then needed to run a charger.  The charger does the charging all the genny provides is the power to do so.  If you are using either to run a typical 30amp smart charger it won&#8217;t even increase the load on the generators.  They will purr like a kitten at that load.</p>
